WEBVTT

00:03:27.600 --> 00:03:31.920
we can help to keep content
accessible for other visitors.

00:03:32.800 --> 00:03:35.496
And by that, it means

00:03:35.520 --> 00:03:39.176
that we can also fight against things

00:03:39.200 --> 00:03:40.840
that we feel are unjust,

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:43.200
like censorship.

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:47.400
In China, the internet
is tightly controlled.

00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:52.456
They can't criticize the government,

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:54.496
organize a protest,

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:57.256
and it's also forbidden to post

00:03:57.280 --> 00:04:01.840
a kind of emoticon to remember the victims
of the Tiananmen Square Massacre.